                <h1>Audience Insights: Who Needs Background Info?</h1>
                <p>The audience that would need the least amount of background information about a subject typically includes those who are already familiar with related topics. For instance, professionals in a specific field or individuals with prior education in the area can quickly grasp new concepts, minimizing the need for extensive explanation.</p>
